article.description: — Khalyl Waters had a career-high 20 points as Troy edged past North Alabama 62-57 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Waters scores 20 to lift Troy over North Alabama 62-57
article.linkText: Waters scores 20 to lift Troy over North Alabama 62-57
article.story: FLORENCE, Ala. -- — Khalyl Waters had a career-high 20 points as Troy edged past North Alabama 62-57 on Thursday night. Zay Williams had 13 points and 13 rebounds for Troy (2-3). Kam Woods and Nick Stampley each had 10 rebounds. Waters hit all 10 of his foul shots. Mervin James and Jamari Blackmon had 11 points for the Lions (2-1). Payton Youngblood had eight rebounds and three blocks. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
